Package gobblin.data.management.version

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DatasetVersion
    Dataset version.
    FileStatusAware
    A FileSystemDatasetVersion that is aware FileStatuss or its paths
    FileSystemDatasetVersion
    Wrapper around Comparable for dataset versions.
    HiveDatasetVersion
    Represents a DatasetVersion for hive partition
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileStatusDatasetVersion
    Implementation of DatasetVersion that uses a single path per version and stores the FileStatus of that path.
    FileStatusTimestampedDatasetVersion
    A TimestampedDatasetVersion that is also aware of the FileStatuss of all its paths.
    StringDatasetVersion
    Dataset version using String as version.
    TimestampedDatasetVersion
    DatasetVersion based on a timestamp.
    TimestampedHiveDatasetVersion
    A HiveDatasetVersion where the version is a timestamp associated with the Partition.
